<p>Hello,</p>

<p>
  You're being paid <%= @payment.amount.format(with_currency: true) %> for
  <i>"<%= @payment.purpose %>"</i> from <%= @payment.event.name %>, but we still
  need a few details from you before we can send it.
</p>

<% days_left = 90 - @reminder_day.to_i %>
<% if days_left > 0 %>
  <p>
    You have <strong>90 days</strong> to accept this payment —
    about <strong><%= days_left %> <%= "day".pluralize(days_left) %></strong> left.
  </p>
<% end %>

<p>Still needed:</p>
<ul>
  <% if @tax_incomplete %>
    <li><%= link_to "Submit your tax information", choose_legal_entity_payee_url(@payment.payee) %></li>
  <% end %>
  <% if @payout_incomplete && @payment.legal_entity.present? %>
    <li><%= link_to "Configure your payout method", legal_entity_url(@payment.legal_entity) %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>
  If you have any questions about this payment, please contact <%= @payment.event.name %>.
</p>

<p>
  Sincerely,
  <br><br>
  The HCB Team
</p>

<p><i class="muted"><%= @payment.event.name %> is fiscally sponsored by The Hack Foundation (d.b.a. HCB), a 501(c)(3) nonprofit (EIN: 81-2908499).</i></p>
